# Trainee Management API

This is a simple Trainee Management Web API developed using ASP.NET Core (.NET).

## Technology Used

### Backend
- .NET 10.0
- C#

### API Tools
- Swagger

### Storage
- In-Memory List (Temporary Data Storage)

---

## Features Completed

- Health Check API
- Add trainees
- View all trainees
- View trainee by ID
- Swagger API testing interface

---

## API Endpoints

### Health Check
- GET `/api/health`

### Trainee APIs
- GET `/api/trainees` → Get all trainees  
- GET `/api/trainees/{id}` → Get trainee by ID  
- POST `/api/trainees` → Create new trainee  


